SaaS-Based RFP System

Overview

The SaaS-Based RFP System is designed to streamline the request for proposal (RFP) process, enabling organizations to efficiently manage RFP creation, vendor responses, evaluation, and selection in a cloud-based environment. This system is scalable, secure, and user-friendly, making it ideal for businesses of all sizes.

Features

Multi-Tenant Architecture: Supports multiple organizations with isolated data per tenant.
Role-Based Access Control (RBAC): Provides granular permissions for Admins, Managers,Accountant and Vendors.

Technology Stack

Backend:

Framework: Node.js with Express

Database: PostgreSQL

ORM: Sequelize

Authentication: JSON Web Tokens (JWT)
